OL,3,CSuicide levels at Leeds Prison a
OL,4,C'critical concern'
OL,6,FThe number of suicides at Leeds Prison
OL,7,Fis a "critical concern", a watchdog
OL,8,Fhas said.
OL,10,FThe Independent Monitoring Board (IMB)
OL,11,Fsaid there were five self-inflicted
OL,12,Fdeaths at HMP Leeds in 2023 and a
OL,13,Ffurther six last year.
OL,15,FIn its annual report the IMB said:
OL,16,F"The large number of self-inflicted
OL,17,Fdeaths in custody at the prison
OL,18,Fcontinues to be a critical concern for
OL,19,Fthe board."
