OL,6,FThere was a total of 16 deaths at the
OL,7,FLeeds prison in the last two years, of
OL,8,Fwhich five were from natural causes.
OL,10,FThe IMB said it was "alarmed" by
OL,11,Freports that monitoring of some
OL,12,Fprisoners known to be at risk of self-
OL,13,Fharm and suicide may not always have
OL,14,Fbeen accurately logged.
OL,16,FThe late arrival of prison transport
OL,17,Fmoving inmates to other establishments
OL,18,For from the courts was a "serious
OL,19,Fconcern".
OL,21,F'Deeply troubling'
