OL,4,C'critical concern'
OL,6,FPrisoners were waiting for long
OL,7,Fperiods in holding rooms awaiting
OL,8,Ftransfer, causing them to become
OL,9,F"frustrated, leading to challenging
OL,10,Fsituations".
OL,12,FThe IMB said a lack of investment was
OL,13,F"exacerbating" overcrowding at the 180-
OL,14,Fyear-old prison.
OL,16,FCampbell Robb, chief executive of the
OL,17,Fsocial justice charity Nacro, said the
OL,18,Ffindings were "deeply troubling".
