OL,3,CSuicide levels at Leeds Prison a
OL,4,C'critical concern'
OL,6,FHe said: "The continued high number of
OL,7,Fself-inflicted deaths is a stark
OL,8,Freminder of a system under immense
OL,9,Fstrain and points to a crucial need
OL,10,Ffor more mental health support.
OL,12,F"Cramped and overcrowded cells are not
OL,13,Facceptable places to house anyone, but
OL,14,Fcan be particularly harmful for people
OL,15,Fwith acute mental health needs. As the
OL,16,FIMB at HMP Leeds rightly points out,
OL,17,Fprison is not ` and should never be
OL,18,Fmistaken for ` a safe alternative to
OL,19,Fproper mental health care."
