OL,6,FHe called for "urgent investment" in
OL,7,Finfrastructure and staffing.
OL,9,FA Ministry of Justice spokesperson
OL,10,Fsaid: "This Government inherited a
OL,11,Fprison system in crisis and we fully
OL,12,Facknowledge the challenges at HMP
OL,13,FLeeds.
OL,15,F"We have taken steps to address the
OL,16,Fnumber of self-inflicted deaths at HMP
OL,17,FLeeds, including improved staff
OL,18,Ftraining and new specialised cells
OL,19,Fwhich ensure constant oversight of
OL,20,Fprisoners who may be at risk."
